      <title>乌克兰盟友预计伊朗将很快向俄罗斯运送导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-allies-expect-iran-to-ship-missiles-to-russia-imminently</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，欧洲官员预计伊朗将很快向俄罗斯运送弹道导弹，此举可能引发乌克兰盟友的迅速反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-allies-expect-iran-to-ship-missiles-to-russia-imminently</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:21:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对以色列人质杀戮的强烈抗议表明内塔尼亚胡的战争代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/israel-hamas-war-outcry-over-hostage-deaths-shows-netanyahu-cost-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末，六名以色列人质在加沙隧道中被发现遭枪杀后，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡做了一件他在 11 个月的战争中从未做过的事 — — 他向遇难者家属道歉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/israel-hamas-war-outcry-over-hostage-deaths-shows-netanyahu-cost-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰要求监禁呼吁处死威尔德斯的巴基斯坦人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/dutch-seek-prison-for-pakistanis-who-called-for-death-of-wilders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰检察官要求对两名巴基斯坦国民判处重刑，一名是宗教领袖，另一名是政客，罪名是煽动其追随者谋杀极右翼议员吉尔特·威尔德斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/dutch-seek-prison-for-pakistanis-who-called-for-death-of-wilders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会紧张局势下，米莱否决阿根廷养老金法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/milei-vetoes-argentina-pension-bill-amid-congressional-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周一否决了一项迫使阿根廷政府提高养老金支付额的法案，这暴露了总统自由党与反对派控制的国会中的盟友之间日益加剧的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/milei-vetoes-argentina-pension-bill-amid-congressional-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西法官批准禁止使用谷歌 X，与马斯克的矛盾进一步加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/brazilian-judges-ratify-ban-on-x-in-deepening-feud-with-musk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院小组的大多数法官确认了一项命令，即禁止埃隆·马斯克的社交网络 X 在巴西使用，并对那些不遵守命令使用虚拟专用网络（VPN）的人处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/brazilian-judges-ratify-ban-on-x-in-deepening-feud-with-musk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称美国钢铁公司应保持国内所有和经营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周一访问匹兹堡期间表示，美国钢铁公司应该继续在国内拥有和运营，这是该公司拟定出售给新日本制铁公司的计划遭遇的最新阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极左翼领导人在州选举后成为权力掮客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/wagenknecht-emerges-as-powerbroker-after-german-state-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管极右翼政党选择党在图林根州周日的州选举中获胜，萨拉·瓦根克内西特 (Sahra Wagenknecht) 和她新组建的极左翼联盟 BSW 将在阻止该党在该州执政方面发挥关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/wagenknecht-emerges-as-powerbroker-after-german-state-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党声称英镑面临威胁，投资者持怀疑态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党声称，如果财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 没有取消养老金领取者的燃料补贴，英国可能面临金融动荡。这一说法受到市场参与者的质疑，其中一人称工党的说法“完全是一派胡言”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/uk-risked-run-on-pound-if-fuel-subsidy-had-stayed-labour-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列允许暂停脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种，加沙开始接种</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-as-israel-allows-pauses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周前，加沙地带一名 10 个月大的婴儿被诊断出患有脊髓灰质炎这种导致瘫痪的疾病。周日，加沙地带启动了针对儿童的脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-as-israel-allows-pauses</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:00:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁巴比斯可能是捷克紧缩政策的最大赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国的中右翼政府将在下一轮预算中加大紧缩措施，此举可能加速民粹主义亿万富翁安德烈·巴比什明年重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
